casebody.data:
K.A.C., Respondent,
v.
Tomas Caesar POPSON, Appellant. WD 81150 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: September 25, 2018
Motion for Rehearing and/or Transfer to Supreme Court Denied November 13, 2018
Application for Transfer to Supreme Court Denied January 29, 2019 K.A.C., St. Petersburg, FL, Respondent, pro se. Tomas Caesar Popson, Excelsior Springs, MO, Appellant, pro se. Before Division Two: Mark D. Pfeiffer, Presiding Judge, and Lisa White Hardwick and Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judges

Order

Per Curiam:

Mr. Tomas Caesar Popson appeals, pro se , from the Judgment of the Circuit Court of Jackson County, Missouri, granting K.A.C. a full order of protection against him. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, a memorandum of law has been provided to the parties. The judgment is affirmed. Rule 84.16(b).
